descriptionHTML:
Chinese New Year is coming soon! Let our Lucky Rooster brings prosperity and happiness for you and your family. Lucky Rooster Watch Face is a simple and minimalistic with animation watch face.

Depending on the set time format, the watch face will display the time in the 12 or 24 hours format while using Digital Format.
Ambient mode are available for battery saving purpose, which display hours and minutes only with black and white color.

Optimized for both round and square display.

Any suggestion or bug, feel free to send it to mailto:trinityxstudio@gmail.com
comments: A very clean and polished watch face for Chinese New Year!
